ActFisheries Act
SubjectApplications for Authorization under Paragraph 35(2)(b) of the Fisheries Act Regulations
PrecisAPPLICATIONS FOR AUTHORIZATION UNDER PARAGRAPH 35(2)(B) OF THE FISHERIES ACT REGULATIONS in order to (1) set out the requirements regarding the information and documentation required for all applications for authorizations under paragraph 35(2)(b) of the Act; and (2) establish procedural requirements and time limits for the processing of these applications.
